Start with an opening logo.
Then open with a text hook that captures the problem users face today. Then introduce using some broll that is related to the pain, then introduce [Feature Name] as the solution.
Show 3 key capabilities with short, clear explanations and product visuals. Focus on how it helps [target audience] achieve [specific outcome] faster or easier.
Tone should feel modern, confident, and innovative — similar to a tech product launch.
Use music and a voiceover that is upbeat.
End with a clear call to action inviting viewers to try the feature or learn more.
Audience: [target user — e.g. marketers, product teams, sales teams]`},{id:"explainer",label:"Educational",defaultTargetLength:"120s",text:`Create an educational explainer video that teaches [topic] to [target audience].
Start with a simple real-world example with broll or question to introduce the topic.
Then explain the concept using clear step-by-step explanations and visual examples.
Break the explanation into 3 simple sections that build on each other.
Use a friendly, helpful tone and avoid jargon.
End with a summary of the key takeaway and what viewers should do next.`},{id:"sales",label:"Sales",defaultTargetLength:"60s",text:`Create a sales video explaining how [product or feature] helps [target customer] solve [specific problem].
Open with a relatable pain point that customers experience today.
Introduce [product] as the solution and highlight 3 concrete benefits customers get from using it.
Focus on business outcomes like saving time, increasing revenue, improving performance, or simplifying workflows.
End with a clear call to action encouraging viewers to book a demo.
Tone: clear, confident, and persuasive without sounding overly promotional.`},{id:"social-media",label:"Social Media",defaultTargetLength:"30s",text:`Create a social media video highlighting [product / insight / tip] for [target audience].
Start with a strong hook in the first 3 seconds that grabs attention.
Deliver one clear insight, tip, or surprising fact related to [topic].
Use fast pacing and visually engaging moments designed for social feeds.
End with a short call to action such as "Learn more," "Try it," or "See how it works."
Tone should feel energetic, modern, and optimized for platforms like LinkedIn, TikTok, and Instagram.`}]},603817,(e,t,r)=>{"use strict";Object.defineProperty(r,"__esModule",{value:!0})},212139,(e,t,r)=>{"use strict";var n,i;Object.defineProperty(r,"__esModule",{value:!0}),r.HtmlCaptureStatus=void 0,(i=n||(r.HtmlCaptureStatus=n={})).Processing="processing",i.Succeeded="succeeded",i.Failed="failed"},7758,(e,t,r)=>{"use strict";Object.defineProperty(r,"__esModule",{value:!0}),r.HUBSPOT_DEAL_SCOPE=void 0,r.dealAccessFromScopes=function(e){return void 0===e?"unknown":e.includes(r.HUBSPOT_DEAL_SCOPE)?"granted":"missing"},r.deriveRequiresReconsent=function(e){return!e.includes(r.HUBSPOT_DEAL_SCOPE)},r.HUBSPOT_DEAL_SCOPE="crm.objects.deals.read"},460502,(e,t,r)=>{"use strict";Object.defineProperty(r,"__esModule",{value:!0})},813589,(e,t,r)=>{"use strict";Object.defineProperty(r,"__esModule",{value:!0})},895916,(e,t,r)=>{"use strict";Object.defineProperty(r,"__esModule",{value:!0})},159787,(e,t,r)=>{"use strict";Object.defineProperty(r,"__esModule",{value:!0})},300797,(e,t,r)=>{"use strict";Object.defineProperty(r,"__esModule",{value:!0}),r.PROMPT_VIDEO_ASSET_PLAYBACK_RATES=void 0,r.transitionSuppressesAnimations=function(e){return!!e&&("fade"===e.type||"crossfade"===e.type||"slide"===e.type||"wipe"===e.type||"iris"===e.type||"cut"===e.type)},r.isImageLogoScene=function(e){return"url"in e&&"string"==typeof e.url},r.PROMPT_VIDEO_ASSET_PLAYBACK_RATES=[.5,1,1.25,1.5,2]},913452,(e,t,r)=>{"use strict";Object.defineProperty(r,"__esModule",{value:!0})},662993,(e,t,r)=>{"use strict";Object.defineProperty(r,"__esModule",{value:!0})},889483,(e,t,r)=>{"use strict";Object.defineProperty(r,"__esModule",{value:!0})},726968,(e,t,r)=>{"use strict";var n,i;Object.defineProperty(r,"__esModule",{value:!0}),r.MemberAccessLevel=void 0,(i=n||(r.MemberAccessLevel=n={})).View="view",i.Edit="edit"},546511,(e,t,r)=>{"use strict";Object.defineProperty(r,"__esModule",{value:!0}),r.SHORTCUT_ENTITY_TYPES